Name: Zolux stainless steel dog bowl
Description:
Zolux stainless steel dog bowl

Stainless steel dog bowls are perfect for holding your dog’s food and water.
They won’t break if dropped or tipped over unlike ceramic bowls and are chew-proof, unlike plastic bowls.
These metal dog bowls don’t hold odours, making them more hygienic than other options.
Stainless steel is considered to be the best material for a dog bowl as it’s easy to clean, doesn’t hold on to bacteria and is much more durable
